one of the things that's weird about technology

00:14:21.149 --> 00:14:25.760
and the communication technology today is
this thing between ephemeral technologies

00:14:25.760 --> 00:14:28.730
and things that last, that stand in the written
record has been very blurred, right?

00:14:28.730 --> 00:14:32.700
And we see this all time where people use
e-mail very ephemerally and it sometimes sticks

00:14:32.700 --> 00:14:34.779
around and gets pulled up in legal discovery.

00:14:34.779 --> 00:14:35.950
