it to say here's how I intend it to be use.

00:17:14.560 --> 00:17:27.569
I think it's a really sort of elegant solution
and we'll see sort of how it -- how it plays

00:17:27.569 --> 00:17:28.569
out.

00:17:28.569 --> 00:17:29.569
Yeah.

00:17:29.569 --> 00:17:33.270
